 * Use this component to add structured data to pages for better SEO.
 * Schema.org markup helps search engines understand page content
 * and can result in rich snippets in search results.
 *
 * Security Note: This uses JSON.stringify which safely escapes all content.
 * The data passed to this component should always be from trusted sources
 * (our own code/database), never from raw user input.
 *
 * @example
 * // In a page or layout:
 * <JsonLd data={websiteSchema} />
 * <JsonLd data={organizationSchema} />
 */

