name: neuman-brain-design-system
description: Complete design system reference for Neuman Brain including brand colors (magenta/cyan/purple gradients), typography (Inter font stack), spacing (4px base unit), component patterns (widgets/modals/buttons), glassmorphism effects, GPU-accelerated animations, and WCAG AA accessibility requirements. Use when implementing UI, choosing colors, applying spacing, creating components, or ensuring brand consistency.
---

# Neuman Brain Design System Reference

**Purpose:** Complete reference for Neuman Brain's design tokens, colors, typography, spacing, components, and code patterns.

**Design Direction:** Option B - Refined Retro-Futurism (November 2025)
- Minimalist black/white base (Atlassian-inspired)
- Strategic magenta/cyan gradients (buttons, hover states, accents)
- Solid backgrounds (no glassmorphism on cards)
- Dark mode: #121212 (dark gray, not pure black)

**See Also:** `.claude/skills/neuman-brain-ux-designer/` for professional design expertise and critique framework.

---

## 🎯 Option B Update (November 2025)

**Major Changes:**
1. **Dark Mode**: Now uses #121212 (dark gray) instead of #000000 (pure black) - easier on eyes
2. **Cards**: Solid backgrounds instead of glassmorphism - better readability
3. **Gradients**: Strategic use only (buttons, hover) - deprecated for backgrounds
4. **Typography**: Improved line heights (1.6 for body text) and limited to 3 font weights

**Result:** Professional aesthetic (like Atlassian, Linear, Height) + Neuman Brain personality (magenta/cyan accents)

---

## 🎨 Brand Identity & Aesthetic

### Visual Aesthetic: Refined Retro-Futurism (Option B)

**Core Philosophy:**
- "Cyberpunk but professional" - edgy but not juvenile
- Retro-futurism - nostalgic tech aesthetic with modern polish
- Privacy-first visual language - locks, shields, local device icons
- Fast & fluid - animations must feel instant, never sluggish

**Brand Narrative:**
> "Your Data. Your Device. Your Second Brain."
>
> Neuman Brain is the ultimate management platform that respects your privacy. Everything runs locally on your device. No cloud required. No tracking. No compromises.

---

## 🎨 Design System

### Color Palette

**Primary Brand Colors:**
```css
/* Neon Magenta (Primary Accent) - from pixelated brain logo */
