--cyan-700: #00C9FF;     /* PRIMARY - secondary brand color */
--cyan-500: #3DD5FF;     /* Bright variant */
--cyan-300: #7FE4FF;     /* Light tints */
--cyan-100: #C2F2FF;
--cyan-50: #E5F9FF;

/* Purple (Gradient Bridge) */
--purple-700: #9333EA;   /* Used in gradient transitions */
--purple-500: #A855F7;
--purple-300: #C084FC;
```

**Neutral Palette:**
```css
/* Black/Gray Neutrals */
--neutral-black: #000000;
--neutral-charcoal: #0D0D0D;
--neutral-graphite: #1A1A1A;
--neutral-darkGray: #2D2D2D;
--neutral-white: #FFFFFF;

